shared.model

Class ResourceList

  • java.lang.Object
    • shared.model.ResourceList

  • public class ResourceList
extends java.lang.Object
    Indicates a list of resources .This is often used to show posessions from player in hand or costs. It tells how many brick,ore,sheep,wool, and wheat are there.
